  <diagram id="voGF98F6_xFp_3yd7J6e" name="Page-4">
    <mxGraphModel grid="0" page="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="681_xqBVxu2jZlwtczqr-2" value="Introduction&lt;div&gt;----------------&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. At the center company logo appears from bottom to upto the center of the page.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. Some animation that explains the unpacking of the offerings of the company.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Replace the compnay icon with an image that represent the Smart city&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Until now, the objective is to explain that our offerings are promoting sustainable smart city solutions.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Estimated Time: 7 Sec&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Blockchain&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;--------------&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. Digital Identiy in the left side&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. then, Digital Data in right Side&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. At the center, the problems in Client Server Architecture like Vulnable to Unauthorized Changes in the data layer. No traceablity of any changes etc&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. Add transaition to replace Digital Data with Cryptographycally protected data and replace the center with Blokchain network.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5. Show that every transaction is singed by the user ( adding motion graphics from left to right )&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;6. Write the benefits of blockchain chain like DLT, Authenticity, Traceability, Immutable&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Estimated Time: 10 Sec&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="110" y="110" width="440" height="398" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="681_xqBVxu2jZlwtczqr-5" value="ICR&lt;div&gt;------------------------------------&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. Show The Product Logo with message &quot;Empowing Intercompany R2R with Blockchain&quot;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. Show Immutable Ledger in the RIght Side&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Show Company A writing signed transactions into the Blockchain (1 Sec)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Likewise show 3 companies in total. (0.5 sec * 2)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. Show smart contracts which will maintain the Netting, Settling of Ledger Accounts in the bottom&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5. Now, (transition) show, the manual excell sheet based solution which are done by a person&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;6. The bottom elements will now reorganized where we will show that Smart Contracts is equivalent to a person and automation on Netting and Settling the transactions&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;7. Shift the page in top direaction and remove the Upper part.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;8. From bottom, we will bring the USPs of the platform like Auditable Data, Traceability by Default, Automation Rule Engine, Minimizing the manual efforts etc.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;9.Now focus on Reporting Part that will be provided by this Plarform (Data Science, Statistics and ML)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Estimated Time: 15 Sec&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="876" y="117" width="440" height="382" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
